query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND kt.kind in ('video movie','tv movie','tv mini series','movie','episode') AND n.gender in ('f') AND (k.keyword like '%revenge%' OR k.keyword like '%alien%' OR k.keyword like '%suspense%' OR k.keyword like '%revengeful%') AND mi_idx.info > '8.0' AND (t.title like '%battle%' OR t.title like '%prophecy%' OR t.title like '%wind%' OR t.title like '%death%' OR t.title like '%comedy%') AND t.production_year < 1992 AND it2.info in ('LD length','LD subtitles','weekend gross','LD sound encoding','mpaa','death date','rentals','LD certification','salary history','LD color rendition','portrayed in','tech info','spouse','birth notes','LD dialogue intellegibility','bottom 10 rank','essays','LD video standard','gross') AND (chn.name like '%Ellen Ripley%' OR chn.name like '%Katniss Everdeen%' OR chn.name like '%Harley Quinn%' OR chn.name like '%Ellen Ripley%' OR chn.name like '%Gamora%') AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','cast','complete')
